Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Icar.\">Icar.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n32035.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be in a death-like swoon,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐξέθανε πεντάκις ὥστε τεθνάναι δοκέειν,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg006.perseus-grc1:5:42\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Epid.\">Epid.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.42</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0487.tlg001:1:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Philem.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.6</biblScope> </bibl> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁ ἐκτεθνεώς,</foreign> opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁ ὄντως τεθνηκώς,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:959a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">959a</biblScope> </bibl> ; opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀποθνῄσκειν,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:521a:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">521a11</biblScope></bibl>, cf.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg036:962b:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pr.\">Pr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">962b4</biblScope> </bibl>:—so in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg001.perseus-grc1:568\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tr.\">Tr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">568</biblScope> </bibl> (though Nessus was really dying) <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐκθνῄσκων</foreign> may retain its usual sense, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fainting away, at the point of death.</tr_> </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n32035.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">become mortified,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸ φλεγμαῖνον ἐκτέθνηκεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg007.perseus-grc1:19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ VC\">VC</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n32035.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c.acc., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be terrified of,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὰς νόσους ἐκτεθνήκασι</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phld.\">Phld.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Herc.\">Herc.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1251.18</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n32035.4\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> later,=<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀποθνῄσκω,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg053:27\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=